age_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 151521, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 好的受教了，虽然我也不知道64位浮点数是啥", "timestamp": 1608198123, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 726792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 151521, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 对，其实就拿了个普通的计算器", "timestamp": 1608198165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 726829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 151521, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 就是你可以计算一下这个结果，然后把它转化成二进制，你会发现转成二进制之后这个数比计算器能表示出的最小的二进制数（受到存储位数限制）还要小，就会输出0", "timestamp": 1608198488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 727053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 151521, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我明白了谢谢大佬！", "timestamp": 1608201384, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 151521, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "今天在外面打工，被旁边两个人问类似怎么算0.0000001/257的问题，因为按计算器算出来是零。真的惊了这也能有工作", "timestamp": 1608196962, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1608201384, "url": "", "vote": {}}}